    <title>About | Astro Blog Review</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="A small Astro prototype for evaluating blog and content admin capabilities."
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <nav>
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      </nav>

      <h1>About This Prototype</h1>

      <p>
        This prototype tests whether Astro can support a Ghost-like blogging
        workflow for this website.
      </p>

      <p>
        It focuses on file-based content, Markdown, MDX, typed frontmatter,
        dynamic routes, tags, drafts, and production build behavior.
      </p>

      <p>
        It does not include a content admin UI. That part requires a CMS
        integration such as Keystatic, Decap CMS, TinaCMS, Sanity, Contentful,
        or Ghost used as a headless CMS.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>